com.github.spring.esdata.loader.junit.jupiter

Annotation Type DeleteEsDataConfig


  • @ExtendWith(value=DeleteEsDataExtension.class)
 @Documented
 @Inherited
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface DeleteEsDataConfig
    @DeleteEsDataConfig is a composed annotation that combines @ExtendWith(DeleteEsDataExtension.class) from JUnit Jupiter with the ability to directly define @DeleteEsData to load.

    It is a shortcut for having both: 
      @ExtendWith(DeleteEsDataExtension.class)
  @DeleteEsData(esEntityClass = BookEsEntity.class, location = "/data/books.json")
  @DeleteEsData(esEntityClass = AuthorEsEntity.class, location = "/data/authors.json.gz")
  public class MyTest{

  }
    See Also:
    ExtendWith, DeleteEsDataExtension, DeleteEsData
